  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Part I: THE LAST SURVIVOR</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2336440/extras/59b54332780775fe290cd52ccc0a251f.poster.avif?t=1770196616\" width=560 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2336440/extras/59b54332780775fe290cd52ccc0a251f.webm?t=1770196616\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2336440/extras/59b54332780775fe290cd52ccc0a251f.mp4?t=1770196616\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Sixteen years have passed since humanity's extinction due to a global virus outbreak. You play as James, who, along with his brother, believes they are the last survivors. However, this changes when he discovers an invitation to a survivors' base, <i>HaustVille</i>. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Part II: WHATEVER IT TAKES</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2336440/extras/4b22d45f093136c9cd4369ec3e94886a.poster.avif?t=1770196616\" width=560 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2336440/extras/4b22d45f093136c9cd4369ec3e94886a.webm?t=1770196616\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2336440/extras/4b22d45f093136c9cd4369ec3e94886a.mp4?t=1770196616\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>Determined to find others, the brothers leave everything behind. After a few days, they reach <i>HaustVille</i>, but something feels wrong about this village. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Part III: THEY ARE GONE</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2336440/extras/2991b1c01668eb3d4140f7e2b143fa95.poster.avif?t=1770196616\" width=560 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2336440/extras/2991b1c01668eb3d4140f7e2b143fa95.webm?t=1770196616\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2336440/extras/2991b1c01668eb3d4140f7e2b143fa95.mp4?t=1770196616\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >\"<i>Where is everyone? What happened here?</i>\" The player must explore HaustVille to uncover the mystery behind the villagers' disappearance and learn more about the virus.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>KEY FEATURES</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2336440/extras/13dda9249cf87d295fee5ad0ab39cb3c.poster.avif?t=1770196616\" width=560 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2336440/extras/13dda9249cf87d295fee5ad0ab39cb3c.webm?t=1770196616\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2336440/extras/13dda9249cf87d295fee5ad0ab39cb3c.mp4?t=1770196616\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Developed using <strong>Unreal Engine 5</strong>, utilizing cutting-edge technology for a fully immersive experience.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The entire village is waiting to be explored. And every place has a story to tell.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Discover the past through environmental storytelling, speech echoes, and objects left behind by other survivors.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A hostile world awaits, where the virus has not only decimated the population but made animals more aggressive. Caution is essential in the wilderness.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Experience cinematic cutscenes that intensify the narrative.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2336440/extras/4380202a6dbe8c8d303340d8a4ea73b7.poster.avif?t=1770196616\" width=560 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2336440/extras/4380202a6dbe8c8d303340d8a4ea73b7.webm?t=1770196616\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2336440/extras/4380202a6dbe8c8d303340d8a4ea73b7.mp4?t=1770196616\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Part I: THE LAST SURVIVOR</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2336440/extras/59b54332780775fe290cd52ccc0a251f.poster.avif?t=1770196616\" width=560 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2336440/extras/59b54332780775fe290cd52ccc0a251f.webm?t=1770196616\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2336440/extras/59b54332780775fe290cd52ccc0a251f.mp4?t=1770196616\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Sixteen years have passed since humanity's extinction due to a global virus outbreak. You play as James, who, along with his brother, believes they are the last survivors. However, this changes when he discovers an invitation to a survivors' base, <i>HaustVille</i>. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Part II: WHATEVER IT TAKES</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2336440/extras/4b22d45f093136c9cd4369ec3e94886a.poster.avif?t=1770196616\" width=560 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2336440/extras/4b22d45f093136c9cd4369ec3e94886a.webm?t=1770196616\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2336440/extras/4b22d45f093136c9cd4369ec3e94886a.mp4?t=1770196616\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>Determined to find others, the brothers leave everything behind. After a few days, they reach <i>HaustVille</i>, but something feels wrong about this village. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Part III: THEY ARE GONE</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2336440/extras/2991b1c01668eb3d4140f7e2b143fa95.poster.avif?t=1770196616\" width=560 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2336440/extras/2991b1c01668eb3d4140f7e2b143fa95.webm?t=1770196616\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2336440/extras/2991b1c01668eb3d4140f7e2b143fa95.mp4?t=1770196616\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >\"<i>Where is everyone? What happened here?</i>\" The player must explore HaustVille to uncover the mystery behind the villagers' disappearance and learn more about the virus.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>KEY FEATURES</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2336440/extras/13dda9249cf87d295fee5ad0ab39cb3c.poster.avif?t=1770196616\" width=560 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2336440/extras/13dda9249cf87d295fee5ad0ab39cb3c.webm?t=1770196616\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2336440/extras/13dda9249cf87d295fee5ad0ab39cb3c.mp4?t=1770196616\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Developed using <strong>Unreal Engine 5</strong>, utilizing cutting-edge technology for a fully immersive experience.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The entire village is waiting to be explored. And every place has a story to tell.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Discover the past through environmental storytelling, speech echoes, and objects left behind by other survivors.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A hostile world awaits, where the virus has not only decimated the population but made animals more aggressive. Caution is essential in the wilderness.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Experience cinematic cutscenes that intensify the narrative.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2336440/extras/4380202a6dbe8c8d303340d8a4ea73b7.poster.avif?t=1770196616\" width=560 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2336440/extras/4380202a6dbe8c8d303340d8a4ea73b7.webm?t=1770196616\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2336440/extras/4380202a6dbe8c8d303340d8a4ea73b7.mp4?t=1770196616\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li></ul>",
